\"to\": 996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his last match\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no way for anyone to be sure if he himself is not.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After collecting his equipment from the sideline, the 38-year-old Spaniard looked around the place that has meant so much to him during his time in tennis and waved to the spectators, who were bidding adieu with the latest in a series of standing ovations for him during these Olympics.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.5643417748731957, \"rank\": 0.7718111746779429, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his equipment\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"the sideline\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectators\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"standing ovations\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal paused before stepping through the doorway that leads toward the locker room and Alcaraz placed his right hand on his partner's left shoulder.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.179660266408309e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadal\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"the doorway\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"the locker room\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"his right hand\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"his partner's left shoulder\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If that's the last time (here) for me, it's an unforgettable feeling and emotions.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last time\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"an unforgettable feeling\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"emotions\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They give me the love and support every single second that I have been on court,\\\" Nadal said about the spectators, who clapped and yelled and sang for him throughout the quarterfinal match.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0379689051517915e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the love\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"every single second\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1658}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectators\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarterfinal match\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's super, super special to feel that, particularly in this place.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this place\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I can not really thank all of them enough for giving me the feelings I have inside myself and the emotions they make me feel,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feelings\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know what's going to happen in the future, but if that's the last time, I enjoyed it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"the last time\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match was played at Court Philippe Chatrier, where French Open finals are contested and where he accumulated more than half of his haul of 22 Grand Slam trophies.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2105, \"end\": 2128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The match\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"French Open finals\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"more than half\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"his haul\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"22 Grand Slam trophies\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me,\\\" Ram said, \\\"Rafa at Roland Garros is the ultimate.\\\"\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ram\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"Rafa\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal has not officially confirmed any details of a possible retirement, but given his age and recent history of injuries \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 including hip surgery in 2023 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it seems safe to say he probably does not have much left in him.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadal\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"any details\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"a possible retirement\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"his age\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"recent history\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"hip surgery\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said Wednesday he doubts he will compete in the U.S. Open, which starts in late August.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Open\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"late August\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I need some time (to decide), but for me, (it) looks difficult,\\\" Nadal said.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0379689051517915e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLO